add_dyldinfo.HelpText: Add symbols from the dyldinfo not already in the symbol table

add_inlinedinfo.HelpText: Add symbols from the inlined libraries, TBD only
add_inlinedinfo.Name: add-inlinedinfo

arch_EQ.HelpText: architecture(s) from a Mach-O file to dump
